# COVID-19 Severity Prediction Tool 

##  Project Overview
This project is a **COVID-19 Patient Severity Prediction Tool** developed as part of **Task 8** of the Machine Learning Internship Program.
The application predicts whether a patient **requires hospitalization** based on clinical symptoms using a trained Machine Learning model and provides **risk level classification**.
The model is deployed as an **interactive web application using Streamlit**.

## Problem Statement
Predict COVID-19 patient severity (Hospitalization Required / Not Required) based on symptoms such as:
- Age
- Fever
- Cough
- Fatigue
- Shortness of Breath

